#spatial points (unprojected)
seaports=gpd.GeoDataFrame(data=infoseaports.copy(),
                           geometry=gpd.points_from_xy(infoseaports.Longitude,
                                                       infoseaports.Latitude), 
                          crs=9252)# notice it is unprojected

# keep Argentina
seaports_arg=seaports[seaports['Country Code']=='Argentina'].copy()

# reset indexes
seaports_arg.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)

# reprojecting
seaports_arg_9252=seaports_arg.to_crs(9252) # projected crs
